Our client is one of the world's most famous Advertising Agencies.
We're looking for a Regional Account Director to lead one of the regions most prominent and famous brands. The right candidate will have 8-10yrs of market leading agency experience you will also be strategic and prepared to work hard and develop award winning work.
Our client is Dubai's leading agency, respected and multi-cultural with at approx 26 different nationalities working in the agency.
We're open to looking solid Account Directors from across the globe and invite you to apply.
Dubai offers an amazing beachside life in a tax free environment. You wont regret the move.
